world 
as we know it], MegaTraveller, Hard Times, and TNE [end of Traveller as we

know it].  Oops, how could I forget Cadillacs and Dinosaurs? [end of
roleplaying
as we know it].  I\'m sorry, but I see a trend here...  [2300AD was omitted
due to
