C     400K    8          E     20.0     200.0
D     450K    9          E     23.0     225.0
E     500K    9          F     25.0     250.0

Volume and price drop 10% per TL above minimum

Passive Sensors
                Minimum
Code  Range     Ship Size   TL   Volume  Cost (MCr)
