> >Performance (Dance)
> >Performance (Drama)
> >Performance (Music)
> >Performance (Writing)
> 
> Nice, but very unimportant for roleplaying in the Traveller millieu, IMHO. Drop.


*very* important to some people.  what if someone wanted to roleplay a
